title: TB Karen's Dilemma | AHS: Double Feature - Episode 1: "Cape Fear" (HQ Clip)
author: AHS Crave
comment: so far this season is amazing, love the characters and I love the story line. Sarah is doing an amazing job portraying TB Karen and Frances is great, probably her best roll. I would love to see more of billie's character Lark and where tf is the chemist, I want to see Angelica Ross so bad!
I saw the first two episodes of AHS Double Feature this morning on Hulu, and so far so great.  It was so good to see Sarah and Evan on here again, along with all the rest of the cast.

Love they brought Macaulay Culkin on.
So far this season is ramping up to something great,  its good so far.
this season is gonna be so good.
Karen is one of my fav characters!!
description: "Cape Fear", the season premiere of American Horror Story: Double Feature (Part 1 - Red Tide) - written by Ryan Murphy & Brad Falchuk, directed by John J. Gray - stars Sarah Paulson as Tuberculosis Karen, Evan Peters as Austin Sommers, Lily Rabe as Doris Gardener, Finn Wittrock as Harry Gardener, Ryan Kiera Armstrong as Alma Gardener, Frances Conroy as Belle Noir, Billie Lourd as Lark, Leslie Grossman as Ursula, Adina Porter as Chief Burelson, Angelica Ross as The Chemist, Macaulay Culkin as Mickey, Denis O'Hare as Holden, and Robin Weigert as Martha. All rights belong to FX Networks and Ryan Murphy Television.
